# Diagrams

Mermaid sources for the LawMitran DevOps documentation. Render with the Mermaid CLI, a Mermaid-aware Markdown viewer, or mermaid.live.

| File | Diagram | Referenced in |
|---|---|---|
| `architecture.mmd` | Overall system architecture | 01-system-architecture.md |
| `aws-infrastructure.mmd` | AWS infrastructure + future migration | 02-aws-infrastructure.md |
| `cicd-pipeline.mmd` | CI/CD pipeline flow | 11-github-actions.md |
| `branch-strategy.mmd` | GitFlow Lite branch graph | 12-branching-strategy.md |

Additional inline Mermaid diagrams live directly in the docs: health-check matrix (16), zero-downtime cutover (17), rollback decision flow (18), monitoring stack (19), and DR runbook (20).

To export PNGs:

```bash
npx -y @mermaid-js/mermaid-cli -i architecture.mmd -o architecture.png
```
